title: AFC, NFC Championship Game Picks with Prisco & RJ (Football 1/18)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco and R.J. White to break down the latest news and notes around the NFL (2:00), their biggest mistake of the Divisional Round (8:45), the Saints vs. Rams NFC Championship Game matchup (12:30), the Patriots-Chiefs AFC Championship Game matchup (24:30) and their exotic picks for the week (40:15).
